## Failure taxonomy

| Failure | When | Maps to (UI) | Recoverable? |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| `NotFound` | requested entity absent | <!-- FILL --> | <!-- FILL --> |
| `Validation` | input fails a business rule | show the rule message | yes |
| `Conflict` | concurrent / duplicate write | <!-- FILL --> | <!-- FILL --> |
| `Persistence` | storage read/write failed | generic retry | maybe |
| `Network` | remote call failed | offline banner / retry | yes |
| `Unexpected` | unhandled | generic error + log | no |
